OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy start with any
OL,6,Fovernight heavy showers quickly dying
OL,7,Fout. The rest of the day will see
OL,8,Fbright and sunny spells developing but
OL,9,Fwith the odd shower possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,12,Fwith some bright spells but soon
OL,13,Fturning cloudier with rain spreading
OL,14,Finto Argyll. Cloudy overnight with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain, possibly heavy, for
OL,16,Fall parts.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,19,Fshowery rain throughout, which will be
OL,20,Fheavy at times, particularly later in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
